column2: SELECT TOP #   a.OBJID AS AKARI_ID,   a.RA AS AKARI_RA,   a.DEC AS AKARI_DEC,	 	      gsl.SpecObjID AS sdssid_gsl,   gsi.SpecObjID AS sdssid_gsi,      gsl.nii_#_flux AS NII_#_FLUX,   gsl.sii_#_flux AS SII_#_FLUX,   gsl.oi_#_flux AS OI_#_FLUX,   gsl.oiii_#_flux AS OIII_#_FLUX,   gsl.h_alpha_flux AS H_ALPHA_FLUX,   gsl.h_beta_flux AS H_BETA_FLUX,      gsl.nii_#_flux_err AS NII_#_flux_err,   gsl.sii_#_flux_err AS SII_#_flux_err,   gsl.oi_#_flux_err AS OI_#_flux_err,   gsl.oiii_#_flux_err AS OIII_#_flux_err,   gsl.h_alpha_flux_err AS H_ALPHA_flux_err,   gsl.h_beta_flux_err AS H_BETA_flux_err     /* into    mydb.AKARIx3#SDSS_lines */  FROM    galSpecLine AS gsl,   galSpecInfo AS gsi  WHERE   gsl.SpecObjID = gsi.SpecObjID
